5.1: Centering Content with justify-content-center and align-items-center
HTML Example (with fixed height for vertical alignment):
<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center" style="height: 200px;">
    <div class="col-6 text-center">
      <div class="p-3 bg-info text-white">Centered Content</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

5.2: Reordering Columns with order-md-*
HTML Example:
<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-2">
      <div class="p-3 bg-warning text-dark text-center">Column A</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-1">
      <div class="p-3 bg-success text-white text-center">Column B</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

